Caster Level(s): Wizard / Sorcerer 5
Innate Level: 5
School: Conjuration
Descriptor(s): Acid
Component(s): Verbal, Somatic
Range: Personal
Area of Effect / Target: Caster
Duration: 1 round / level
Save: No
Spell Resistance: No

This spell creates an acid shield around your person. Any creature striking you with its body does normal damage, but at the same time the attacker takes 2 points per caster level of acid damage ( Maximum 30 points ).